  "title": "GROUND IMPROVEMENT WORK MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>JAK ENGINEERING & CONSTRUCTION PTE. LTD.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will apply your expertise in ground improvement techniques to manage project quotations, tender submissions, and client coordination, ensuring efficient execution and delivery of engineering solutions.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Apply ground improvement knowledge to prepare accurate project quotations and bills of quantity that support successful tender submissions</li><li>Manage submission of claims and prepare detailed schedules of payment to ensure timely financial processing</li><li>Coordinate effectively with clients to align project execution with their requirements and expectations</li><li>Oversee executive work related to ground improvement projects, ensuring quality and compliance with standards</li><li>Utilize knowledge of grouting machinery to supervise machinery operation, maintenance, and repair activities</li><li>Arrange for spare parts procurement and manage machinery repair schedules to minimize downtime</li></ul>",
